metadata.name: The Golden Swan
metadata.description:
"Revealed against  
The waters with  
The subtle substance  
Of a myth,

A myth not fully  
Known to men,  
She floats, she glides, she lives again!"

The Swan  
BY MABEL SIMPSON


This is my first piece using Manifold. 
Applying "The Pareto principle" I decided to combine Midjourney AI and painted over using Clip Studio Paint and Adobe Photoshop. 

Holders who mint 3 or more editions will be gifted a new piece. The work won't be available anywhere else. That way I want to thank everyone who supported me throughout the years and still value my works and my art journey. 
Thank you for believing in me.
